---
title: Double Seared Beef & Roast Veggie Israeli Couscous with Tahini Yoghurt
description: There are sunny days ahead when it’s steak on the menu, add some garlic and herb seasoning to elevate it and drizzle over a tahini yoghurt. Keep the warm vibes going with an Israeli couscous tossed through with roasted veggies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/654db1a102458a46e49a898d-7115ca3b.jpeg
